projectDesc: A real-time web chat application built using React and WebSocket. It allows users to communicate in real-time with features like private messaging and emoji support.
An e-commerce platform developed using Django for backend and JavaScript for frontend. The platform includes features such as product catalog, shopping cart, and order processing.
Personal portfolio website built with React and TypeScript. The website showcases projects, skills, and provides a way for visitors to contact the owner.
A simple blog platform with Node.js backend and Express.js for API. Users can create, edit, and delete blog posts, and the platform supports user authentication.
Task management application using Java and Spring Boot. The app allows users to create tasks, set deadlines, and mark tasks as completed, helping in effective task organization.
Weather application built with Vue.js and consuming a weather API. Users can check the current weather conditions, forecast, and get weather information for specific locations.
Dashboard for managing social media accounts using React. The dashboard integrates with various social media platforms, allowing users to schedule posts and track engagement.
Recipe application with Python backend using Flask framework. Users can browse recipes, search for specific dishes, and save their favorite recipes for later.
Job board application built with Angular for the frontend. The platform connects job seekers with employers, providing a seamless interface for job postings and applications.
Database of movies created with React and fetching data from a movie API. Users can search for movies, view details, and discover new releases in the world of cinema.
